---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-ornament">✦</div>
	<div class="footer-cta">
		<p class="cta-eyebrow">¿Listo para comenzar?</p>
		<h3>Agenda una sesión con Juan Pablo</h3>
		<p class="cta-desc">Terapeuta de Regresión a Vidas Pasadas con años de experiencia acompañando procesos de sanación profunda.</p>
		<a href="https://www.juanpabloloaiza.com/agenda" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-btn">
			Reservar mi sesión →
		</a>
	</div>
	<div class="footer-bottom">
		<div class="footer-links">
			<a href="/">Inicio</a>
			<span>·</span>
			<a href="/blog">Artículos</a>
			<span>·</span>
			<a href="https://www.juanpabloloaiza.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">juanpabloloaiza.com</a>
		</div>
		<p class="footer-copy">© {today.getFullYear()} Juan Pablo Loaiza · Todos los derechos reservados</p>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(184, 149, 42, 0.15);
		margin-top: 4em;
	}

	.footer-ornament {
		text-align: center;
		color: #D4AF6A;
		font-size: 1.2em;
		padding: 1.5em 0 0;
		letter-spacing: 0.5em;
	}

	.footer-cta {
		background: #F5EFE0;
		padding: 3em 2em 3.5em;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(184,149,42,0.12);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,149,42,0.12);
		margin-top: 1em;
	}

	.cta-eyebrow {
		font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
		font-size: 0.7em;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #A89060;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}

	.footer-cta h3 {
		font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
		font-size: 1.4em;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: #2C1F0E;
		margin-bottom: 0.75em;
	}

	.cta-desc {
		color: #7A6840;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		max-width: 480px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.75em;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		background: #B8952A;
		color: #fff;
		font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
		font-size: 0.82em;
		font-weight: 500;
		padding: 0.8em 2.25em;
		border-radius: 4px;
		text-decoration: none;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		transition: background 0.2s;
	}

	.cta-btn:hover {
		background: #8B6914;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.footer-bottom {
		background: #FDFAF4;
		padding: 1.5em 1.5em 2.5em;
		text-align: center;
		color: #A89060;
		font-size: 0.82em;
	}

	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.75em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}

	.footer-links a {
		color: #A89060;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.footer-links a:hover { color: #8B6914; }

	.footer-links span { color: #D4C090; }

	.footer-copy { margin: 0; color: #C0A870; }
</style>
